Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:43.02,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something Given (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}December.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Christmas was approaching,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got another call\Nfrom my foster sister, Kyouko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot something? A watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.\NGotou just gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He gets mad if I don't wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I might have gotten a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to wait\Nat the Mec in front of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it, that place is way too noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't I have gone to your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about I guess\Nwhat you were just thinking? Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just joking. You look so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing for New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}No. I have a lot of matches coming up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}so I need to focus on practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your last match of the year is the rank-deciding\None against Mr. Yasui on the 24th, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of Mr. Yasui,\Nit seems he's finally getting divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:04:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's usually a meek, modest guy. But when he\Nloses, he drinks, gets crazy, and gambles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised his wife put up with it\Nfor this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for his daughter the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She must've been scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, living under the same roof with\Na father who breaks bad every time he loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, I hate this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I hear the daughter had one wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She said,\N"I want to be with Papa until Christmas."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't stand it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It brings tears to your eyes. Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The way she speaks,\Nher words sticking to me like glue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rei, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But more than anything...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...her words that drip with poison...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your scarf will blow away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should wrap it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I hate myself for wanting to hear it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Children have it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, they can't choose their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. But come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it was different for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You chose your own parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You chose somebody else's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad, can we open them now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what is this giant teddy bear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:32.16,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pow\NPow\NPow
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:32.16,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!\NTake that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, Dad! I'm in middle school now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Game Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For a child of this family...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or anyone striving\Nto be a professional shogi player...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the value of those beautiful pieces...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...their meaning...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the father's feelings...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...were unmistakable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should I have gotten you a toy, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was unmistakable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How my foster brother and sister\Nwere very hurt then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's sad, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A papa who comes home after winning,\Nor a papa who comes home after losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which would be more fitting\Nas a final Christmas memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from P.E. and music, not bad, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your grades for math and physics\Nare awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Report Card
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That being said, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to be in Sendagaya by 9:30, right?\NYou should hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:50.74,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you're a busy guy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You even have matches\Nup until Closing Ceremonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You barely met\Nthe required attendance days this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but you may be in trouble if your matches\Nincrease third term. So be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ehhh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to lose?\NBut my living is on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}1-B Christmas Party
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, after the Closing Ceremony today,\Nthe kids in the class
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are having a Christmas party, apparently.\NDid you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course I didn't know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess there's only one thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After your match is over,\Nwhy don't you come back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:31.91,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit,\Nthey didn't\Ninvite me\Neither.\NWhy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just us crummy guys,\Neating cake while playing shogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.91,DefaultLef2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Answer: You're a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I turn around and he's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Eeeeek!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!\NThis just makes me a mean old teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen until I'm done talking!\NPlease, Kiriyama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When did it start?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When did Christmas become painful for me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:07:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A certain thought crossed my mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"It's like a report card."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From that year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that year, how much love did I receive\Nfrom friends, family and my parents?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How did they express that love for me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yasui 6th-Dan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}The doors are closing. Please be careful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The daughter said, "I want to be\Nwith Papa until Christmas."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Until Christmas..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A papa who comes home after winning,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or a papa who comes home after losing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which would be more fitting\Nas a final Christmas memory?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, Rei?{\i0}
