Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:32.12,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something Given (Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want to say I gave up\Nin the middle of the game, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:13:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The match with Mr. Yasui ended all too soon\Nthat late afternoon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After 8-f-Pawn, I could've surprised you,\Ntaking your knight at 9-e...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could've gone that way.\NIf I'd noticed, I would've done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't notice, so it can't be helped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You might've seen it, but I didn't see it,\Nso what good is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Yasui continued muttering,\Nas if he was talking to himself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was unsettled by the faint smell\Nof alcohol on his breath as he sighed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The match began slowly and quietly\Nwith a Yagura Opening.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Carefully... Carefully..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From the way he played,\NI could almost hear him telling that to himself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Don't make a mistake. Don't make a mistake."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shogi Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...after the lunch break,\NMr. Yasui made a mistake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After a short pause, he noticed it, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But afterwards, if he attacked the king\Nfrom 8-f-Pawn, who knows?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he then pulled his knight back and\Nheld out, which side would victory tilt towards?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But then I could see Mr. Yasui's silhouette\Nlose strength and weaken.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not like the possibilities\Nhave all disappeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hear the daughter had one wish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait a second! Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That easily?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't let go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your focus, your awareness...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I want to be with Papa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't give up such precious things so easily!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...until Christmas."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm begging you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't let go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shogi Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I think that's enough for a post-match review.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yasui! Mr. Yasui!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which way did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There he is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where's he going?\NThe station isn't that way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yasui!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:17:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yasui!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Shut up, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this was our last Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's your own fault for being weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You lost because you were weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Practice! I can tell when you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you say "I know, but I can't," then just quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For me, everything's on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't have anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing but shogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink booze to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no use for weak players!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.78,0:22:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...then why...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.30,0:22:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I said I had no reason to fight,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but the truth is,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that a beast lives within me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.39,0:22:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}It's a rampaging beast that would bite off\Neverything in sight to survive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.02,0:22:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the battle begins, no matter what,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}its hand reaches out\Ntowards the path of survival.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.65,0:22:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if it means misery for others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.03,0:22:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what kind of world awaits...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:23:00.04,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something Given (Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:35.31,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 11
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.72,0:24:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Rei's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.72,0:24:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Rei.\NStretch out your neck, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.93,0:24:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei? Rei, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.06,0:24:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.40,0:24:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.19,0:24:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.\NI wanted you to come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.61,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.86,0:24:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode of\N"March Comes in Like a Lion".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.24,0:24:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope everyone watches\Nour great performances!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.45,0:24:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mr. Hayashida...
